title: Etiquette dinner scheduled for students to gain professional dining experience (Penn State Lehigh Valley)
text: ( Source : Penn State Lehigh Valley ) A diverse group of alumni will be seated with the students at each table to provide advice on professional conversation and proper exchanges for future business lunches and dinner that students may attend
